definitions.definition: An extremely durable timber highly valued for shipbuilding and other purposes , yielded by Tectona grandis (and Tectona spp.).
A tree of the species in the genus Tectona .
A yellowish brown colour, like that of teakwood .

main_definition: ( uncountable , countable ) An extremely durable timber highly valued for shipbuilding and other purposes , yielded by Tectona grandis (and Tectona spp.).
secondary_definitions: ( countable ) A tree of the species in the genus Tectona .
( uncountable ) A yellowish brown colour, like that of teakwood .
